[spoiler title='Explanation']

We'll start with a variable `word` which is initially empty. Next we'll iterate our string, if we encounter a `word` we print the value from the variable `word` and set its contents to empty. If we encounter something else we add that character to our `word`. We'll also have to print the word one last time outside the loop.

[/spoiler]

